imize the value based on the pieces cut. The longer, the more expensive."],"metadata":{"id":"-MjClD_W_Rv2"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["#### Value scale:\n","#### Length: 1   2   3   4   5   6   7   8\n","#### $Price_:  1   5   8   9  10  13  16  20"],"metadata":{"id":"7_YRdRE__Zcx"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["#### Function Definition"],"metadata":{"id":"f4hnMlhUDNKi"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["def bar_cut(lengths, prices, n):\n","  \"\"\" Args: lenghts = list of possible lenghts,\n","            prices = values to make,\n","            n = length of rod \"\"\"\n","# Create a table to store maximum values for different lengths\n","  dp = [0] * (n + 1)  # Initialize the table with zeros\n","# Fill the table using dynamic programming\n","  for i in range(1, n + 1):\n","      print(i)\n","      max_value = -1\n","      for j in range(i):\n","          max_value = max(max_value, prices[j] + dp[i - j - 1])\n","          print(\"max_value =\",max_value,\n","                \"j =\",j)\n","      dp[i] = max_value\n","  return dp[n]"],"metadata":{"id":"dPKExVxD8uXg","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1723306058776,"user_tz":180,"elapsed":440,"user":{"displayName":"Andre Marques","userId":"13386997495052440502"}}},"execution_count":7,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["#### Example"],"metadata":{"id":"G_tlqW_CDSeT"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["lengths = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8]\n","prices = [1,5,8,9,10,13,16,20]\n","rod_length = 8\n","result = bar_cut(lengths, prices, rod_length)\n","print(\"Maximum value:\", result)"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"b4fZk56jBcwh","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1723306179523,"user_tz":180,"elapsed":314,"user":{"displayName":"Andre Marques","userId":"13386997495052440502"}},"outputId":"8391f277-db2f-41a8-a126-640c674faf4e"},"execution_count":10,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["1\n","max_value = 1 j = 0\n","2\n","max_value = 2